videos.headline: S. Gibbs Steal leads to made Layup.

videos.description: 1H (8:51) UCF A.J. Davis made Three Point Jumper. Assisted by Matt Williams.
videos.headline: A. Davis made Three Point Jumper. Assisted by M. Williams.

videos.description: UCF's Daiquan Walker throws up the lob to Tacko Fall, who is just too tall for everyone, to make the huge alley-oop dunk.
videos.headline: Easy to throw alley-oops with a 7-foot-6 dunker

videos.description: On the fast break, UConn's Jalen Adams finds a hard charging Amida Brimah who throws down the huge two-handed slam.
videos.headline: Streaking Brimah tries to destroy the rim

videos.description: 2H (7:24) CONN Daniel Hamilton made Three Point Jumper. Assisted by Rodney Purvis.

videos.description: Senior Omar Calhoun checks out of game on Senior Day, fans chant: "Thank you, Omar"
videos.headline: Senior Omar Calhoun checks out of game on Senior Day, fans chant: "Thank you, Omar"

videos.description: UConn's Rodney Purvis throws up the perfect lob to Kentan Facey for the huge alley-oop to highlight the Huskies' blowout win over UCF.
videos.headline: Facey punctuates win with monstrous alley-oop

videos.description: Senior Shonn Miller checks out of game on Senior Day

videos.description: Senior reserve Nnamdi Amilo scores on Senior Day, UConn bench dabs to celebrate
videos.headline: Senior reserve Nnamdi Amilo scores on Senior Day, UConn bench dabs to celebrate

videos.description: Malcolm Huckaby and Jason Bennetti break down Connecticut's win over Central Florida in the Huskies' final regular-season game to go into the AAC tourney on a high note.
videos.headline: UConn routs UCF in must-win game
